snippet.title: SolSeraph | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
SolSeraph is now available on the PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and Steam for PC for $14.99! Balancing side-scrolling action and top-down strategy elements, you must guide each tribe from the clouds above in order to help expand their territory, dispel the dark fog that shrouds their lands, and seal the monster lairs hiding therein as Helios, the Knight of Dawn.

Official website: https://www.sol-seraph.com/
